you. It should be Churchill.

1296
01:31:05,594 --> 01:31:08,598
He's the midwife who delivered you
your Pakistan.

1297
01:31:09,364 --> 01:31:13,403
I did what any leader would do
to realise his people's dreams.

1298
01:31:14,569 --> 01:31:17,379
