on its emergence among the family
of nations.

1310
01:32:00,816 --> 01:32:05,492
Long years ago we made a tryst
with destiny,

1311
01:32:05,554 --> 01:32:10,299
and now the time comes when
we shall redeem our pledge.

1312
01:32:10,692 --> 01:32:15,505
